{
    "name": "Arboreal Copse",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Arboreal Copse",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Though arboreal wardens typically remain within the boundaries of the forests they protect, they occasionally gather into copses to seek information about potential threats to report back to arboreal regents. Arboreals are typically slow to act, but copses must sometimes make quick judgment calls when faced with imminent dangers.",
